description: Betty Cooper has quite a green thumb! She's the best gardener at Riverdale High and loves sharing her tips with the rest of the gang -- even though they don't always do so well at it! Join Betty in this digital-only collection of leafy green stories!
name: Betty's Garden Variety

description: Tenma and Oto are on their true first date since they started dating for real. But when they run into Haruto and Megumi at the amusement park, Megumi suggests they go on a double date. Haruto seems more interested in challenging Tenma to battles on the rides, but his plans flop disastrously. Having lost all hope, he gets on the Ferris wheel...only to find himself alone with Oto!
name: Chapter 29

description: Evelyn and Frank hide out in the best place to go unnoticed in Los Angeles: the public library. Frank makes a call that could safeguard their lives... or endanger them.
name: Chapter Four: Angel's Flight

description: Being Spider-Man can be tough—Peter Parker never knows when the next call to action will come…but sometimes it's also totally awesome! Like when Peter shows up to lend a hand— to none other than Iron Man himself! IRON MAN AND SPIDER-MAN TEAM-UP TIME!

In the aftermath of the epic war amongst current the WWE Superstars and WWE Legends, most of the WWE Universe has returned to normal. But an eclectic group including Shawn Michaels, Dolph Ziggler, the British Bulldog, Roman Reigns, and Bruno Sammartino have been left behind to face the dangers of a desolated Battleground. Michaels and Reigns must unite their team if all are to survive their deadly situation and uncover a way off the planet. But Bray Wyatt has plans of his own and has recruited the likes of Brock Lesnar, Larry Zbysko, Cesaro, and Greg "The Hammer" Valentine to his insane cause - one that calls for the elimination of anyone who won't swear allegiance to his ways.

Note: The digital edition (6/28/2016) for this volume was released before the print edition.

description:
Welcome, please take your greasy ticket stub and box of warm, stale popcorn with you ,the show is about to begin. Enjoy a front row seat to the biggest names in comics delivering tales that will grab you by the gut and tie you in knots. These are the horror stories of Cinema Purgatorio. Illustrated in stark moody black & white, each issue is perfect-bound, with no ads, and all of the works are very long-form, meaning there are no collections planned before 2018. Jump in now and embrace the new future of comics. The one of which Alan Moore has always dreamed. It's here, now. Hiding in the dark corner. Welcome to Cinema Purgatorio.

Led by Batwoman and Renee Montoya, the rebel group makes a run for it to the coast, but there they find themselves trapped and surrounded!
name: Chapter 50

description: From the Harley Quinn team of Jimmy Palmiotti and Justin Grey! In a future when technology can implant or remove human memories and police use brain scan technology in criminal investigations, a mute girl and a simpleton handyman discover they both have secrets that will either save or destroy them. Spencer and Kalina are hounded by a powerful senator who will stop at nothing to recover the memories planted in Kalina's head, memories that threatens to ruin his career and send him to jail for life.

...And the door will open, part 4

Lilia Romanova's life of late has become a total chaos. For example, right now a battle broke at her door between mysterious lumberjacks and wizard Arthur. Just a few minutes ago the fair-haired wizard lost both of his hands, but it doesn't seem to stop him...
name: ...And the door will open Part 4

description: Wonder Woman has been making a big splash in the European Theater of Operations, and it’s drawn the notice of Nazi high command—and something even scarier. Plus, Steve Trevor is teaching Diana Prince to fly an airplane, without knowing that his admiration for Wonder Woman is making things awkward for his trainee!

Breakthrough, part 2

After successfully completing another task, Meteora gets a decent reward, which she's planning to spend on yet another breakthrough - an attempt to literally break through the preliminary space isolation and return to the Earth, her home planet. Unfortunately, Meteora gets caught by the members of the Union of Justice and Order. And then Zab Neru, Military Commissioner for the Coalition appears. According to him, Ora's "breakthroughs" caused irreparable damage to the Coalition budget, so this time the punishment will be a lot more severe than usual - he sentences Ora to death by the split into atoms!
name: Breakthrough Part 2

description: Celebrating the Fourth of July is complicated enough for a patriotic symbol turned soviet assassin, but then Hydra agents had to go and rob the Winter Soldier's secret storage locker. Who sent them? What do they want? Bucky doesn't care — he just wants his #$%& back.

volume.name: A Year Of Marvels: July Infinite Comic

description: It has been four years since the dwarf king Magni Bronzebeard sought to protect his world and was cursed, frozen as a solid diamond statue at the center of Old Ironforge. When he emerges from his crystal slumber with a dire warning of dark times to come, will his daughter, Moira, be able to set aside the pain of her past and forgive Magni to help unite her people?
name: Magni: Fault Lines
